item.description: I’m a sports scientist and athletic performance coach based in Sydney, Australia. I post my work and ideas on maximising sports performance on this site, my Twitter, or my Youtube channel. My employment and education history can be found in my one-page résumé or my full CV. Feel free to contact me via email or DM me through any of my social media accounts on the home page of this site.

item.title: First post
item.description: Hugo is the world’s fastest framework for building websites. It is written in Go. It makes use of a variety of open source projects including: https://github.com/russross/blackfriday https://github.com/alecthomas/chroma https://github.com/muesli/smartcrop https://github.com/spf13/cobra https://github.com/spf13/viper Learn more and contribute on GitHub.
